        <h2>Process Monitor for Windows</h2>
        <div class="summary">
            <div>
                <p>Monitor CPU, memory, disk, and thread metrics in real-time for running applications.
                    Quickly identify resource bottlenecks, memory leaks, and performance spikes without
                    interrupting your workflow. The graphical interface shows exactly what's happening
                    when performance issues occur.</p>
                <p>Built for developers, <strong>appstat</strong> combines detailed monitoring with a clean interface. Select any running application to see its performance data instantly. Features include dark/light modes, always-on-top option, and exportable logs for team analysis.</p>
                <p>
                    <strong>appstat is freeware.</strong>
                    You can use <strong>appstat</strong> on any computer, including a computer in a commercial organization.
                    <strong>There is no need to register or pay to use the software.</strong>
                </p>
